ting a significant positive relationship between agricultural biodiversity of the household with dietary adequacy of the child's diet. Important significant relationships were found in this study: between agricultural biodiversity and dietary adequacy; between agricultural biodiversity and household food security and between dietary adequacy and household food security. Furthermore, the effect of seasonality on household food security and nutrient intake was illustrated.},
